member.name: FILE_LEVEL_TRIM_OUTPUT
member.summary: Used as output to theFSCTL_FILE_LEVEL_TRIM control code.

member.name: FILE_LEVEL_TRIM_OUTPUT.NumRangesProcessed
member.summary: Contains the number of ranges that were successfully processed. This may be less than the value passed in the NumRanges member of theFILE_LEVEL_TRIM structure. If it is then the last ranges in the array were not processed.
